[[File:LukeWorried.jpg|{{AltFloat}}|Cage learns details about his [[Reva Connors|wife]]'s death]]
Having caught up with Jones at [[Serena Grier's Apartment]] where she was handing over Antoine, Cage confronted Jones about leaving him. Grier handed over a file with the information Cage wanted, but Jones tried to convince him that it may not be worth finding out as it would only hurt him and those around him. Cage ignored her pleas and opened the file, learning that the bus driver, [[Charles Wallace]], was drunk when he caused the crash that killed his [[Reva Connors|wife]] and was still working. Furious, Cage stormed out to hunt down Wallace.{{Ref|JJ106}}

