{{Quote|You made me think I could get past it, did [[Kilgrave]] force you to do that? You let me be inside you. You touched me with the same hands that killed my [[Reva Connors|wife]], while you knew."<br>"I'm so sorry|Luke Cage and [[Jessica Jones]]|AKA You're a Winner!}}
